Package: topografie
Type: Package
Title: This package makes it easy to study topography
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hans Weda
Maintainer: Hans Weda <hansweda@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains a shiny app that allows easy studying of topography.
    The app shows a map (of Europe) in which one element (city, country, river, sea, mountain range) 
    is highlighted. The user (student) needs to select the correct name for this element.
